snippet.textDisplay: Made in Bangladesh. There is no friendship with a neighbor where no mutual respect is given. You can't be coming inside our border chasing down two of our shepherd boys and taking a shot at them. And you expect to be friendly with you. Good luck with that. Made in Bangladesh will thrive. Joy Bangla. 🇧🇩🇧🇩
